<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application>gst-plugins</application></title>

<para>Installez <application>gst-plugins</application> en lançant les commandes suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=`pkg-config --variable=prefix ORBit-2.0` \
    --sysconfdir=/etc/gnome &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install &amp;&amp;
gst-register</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>
